title.narrative: Haiti: Immediate Response Operations Team and Goods in Kind Costs

description.narrative: This activity (Haiti: Immediate Response Operations Team and Goods in Kind Costs) is a component of Response to Haiti Earthquake: January 2010 reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £4,328,054. This component benefits Haiti, and works in the following sector(s): Material relief assistance and services . , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 13-01-2010 and the end date is 31-03-2012.
